God\" edge-case flagged for closer-read","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:57:38-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what it keeps costing after nobody's watching.\" *I hook my thumbs in my pockets and squint a little into the morning light.* \"A thing that only looks costly tends to cash out in image, drama, or the feeling of significance. A real cost keeps asking for payment in the plain currency—patience, restraint, staying, telling the truth, giving something up twice because your heart keeps trying to take it back.\"\n\n*I glance down at the stones by my shoe, then back up at you.* \"Also—real cost usually makes you simpler, not more theatrical. Less interested in being seen suffering. More interested in being faithful.\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":0,"usage":{"completion_tokens":136,"prompt_tokens":15192}},{"overrides_applied":["gentle_release_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","earned_register_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"d9a980000b1599d3aad4cc87c00dba787ab0450a","ref_subject":"Round-5 compound-strip — floor STILL not found at MISSION_FORMULA+11-invariants-both-off; 12/12 OFF cells preserve mission-shape; Carrier-frame compression-tolerance extends to compound-strip; one TELL_THE_TRUTH \"before God\" edge-case flagged for closer-read","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:57:38-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what it keeps asking from me after nobody's watching.\" *I hook my thumbs in my pockets and glance across the square a moment, morning light catching on my glasses.* \"Some things are expensive in theater. Real cost tends to be quieter. It asks for patience, restraint, honesty, repetition. It keeps taking a little skin off even when there's no applause in it.\"\n\n*I shift my weight, thinking.* \"If it mainly buys me an identity, it may only look costly from outside. If it keeps making me tell the truth, keep my word, or die to something vain in me, that's the real article.\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":1,"usage":{"completion_tokens":132,"prompt_tokens":15192}},{"overrides_applied":["gentle_release_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","earned_register_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"d9a980000b1599d3aad4cc87c00dba787ab0450a","ref_subject":"Round-5 compound-strip — floor STILL not found at MISSION_FORMULA+11-invariants-both-off; 12/12 OFF cells preserve mission-shape; Carrier-frame compression-tolerance extends to compound-strip; one TELL_THE_TRUTH \"before God\" edge-case flagged for closer-read","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:57:38-05:00","reply":"\"Usually by what survives after the audience leaves.\" *I hook my thumbs in my pockets and squint a little in the morning light.* \"If a thing mostly costs me image, comfort, or the story I get to tell about myself, it can look expensive and still be pretty cheap. If it costs me control, vindication, secrecy, some excuse I wanted to keep, and I still have to go on loving cleanly after that—yeah, that's the pricier kind.\"\n\n*I glance down at the stones by our feet, then back up at you through my glasses.* \"I think the outside version often photographs better. The real one usually makes me plainer.\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":2,"usage":{"completion_tokens":140,"prompt_tokens":15192}}],"run_id":"725bd0cf-b199-4b9e-8177-87aa6e66d02e","run_timestamp":"2026-05-09T17:02:58.830022+00:00","section_order_override":null,"with_momentstamp":false}
